    ktorrent

        # Torrent client configuration
        1. Maximum upload speed
        80% of your maximum upload speed

        2. Maximum download speed
        95% of your maximum download speed

        3. Maximum connected peers per torrent
        upload speed * 1.3

        4. Maximum upload slots
        1 + (upload speed / 6)

